  <description>
    <p>
      Zerra System Cleaner is a professional, lightweight system cleaning utility for Linux desktops. 
      It provides a safe and efficient way to recover disk space by identifying and removing redundant files 
      without compromising system stability.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>APT Environment: Clean package archives and cache</li>
      <li>System Maintenance: Remove redundant logs and vacuum journald</li>
      <li>Application Hygiene: Clear browser caches (Firefox, Chrome) and thumbnails</li>
      <li>Intelligent Automation: Schedule maintenance based on idle time or disk usage</li>
      <li>Detailed History: Track every cleaning operation and space recovered</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
